snippet.title: Pussy Puzzle 🐈🧩 | OFFICIAL Release Trailer
snippet.description:

Available for 🖼️, 🐧 and 🍎

Now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1196280/Pussy_Puzzle/
